{"tid":922164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★輸錢反枱！聲稱「無風險」200名港人投資被騙向議員求助，苦主斥世界大騙案","createTime":"2018-11-30T06:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T11:35:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"206515c747780e9423ad7ebfb39fd398d177666a","tid":922164,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2155189/org/28ea69df55b4929bc4a25fb35cc25380.jpg/nzfJiL5Wd_RNwOUdK__vQwMyTxvQ48nVdbzzlHW885Q?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2155189%2Forg%2F28ea69df55b4929bc4a25fb35cc25380.jpg%2FnzfJiL5Wd_RNwOUdK__vQwMyTxvQ48nVdbzzlHW885Q%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=00a3d6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投資陷阱無處不在，民建聯立法會議員梁志祥指近日接獲市民求助，指有涉及欺詐成分的投資公司負責人帶錢潛逃，事件涉及金額可能高達10億港元，受害人多達200名，並已報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n有苦主直斥「世界大騙案」，指投資公司聲稱其「無風險」債券不能以私人名義購買，而他們只會幫熟人購買，在建立信任下不虞有詐，怎料血汗錢卻被一舖清袋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2155003/org/bf299f239e172495444114d29f5cd15d.jpg/30XeyqPwmJOrsDn1ReSXR_mNdkvlQ3wC_fh_7f34f-0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2155003%2Forg%2Fbf299f239e172495444114d29f5cd15d.jpg%2F30XeyqPwmJOrsDn1ReSXR_mNdkvlQ3wC_fh_7f34f-0&h=543c7fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n苦主李小姐（化名）去年在朋友介紹下，認識一名投資公司負責人賴先生，對方聲稱其協助投資的債券不能以私人名義購買，強調「唔會打廣告，只會幫熟人」、「外面唔係咁容易買到」，又聲稱希望幫她賺取利息，加上賴先生曾在中資機構工作，故在信任下購買投資期為一年債券，年利率為12%，但簽署的並非投資合約，而是借錢給該公司投資的合約。<br />\n<br />\n她說，投資入場門檻最少要100萬元，過去投資回報穩定，故不虞有詐，並提早在本月與對方續約投資，對方卻把其血汗錢帶走，直斥「世界大騙案」。<br />\n<br />\n苦主被「彈票」揭發投資金被清空<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員梁志祥表示，有投資逾300萬元苦主近日因急需錢買樓，希望向投資公司取回本金及利潤，在周二（27日）被「彈票」才揭發投資戶口的錢已被取走，這位賴先生也逃去無蹤，靠朋友間互相通傳下，其他苦主才獲悉被騙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁指出，這兩間公司有十多年投資經驗，涉及中港及海外投資者，債券投資期由3星期至1年不等，平均有2.4%利率回報，估計苦主損失數百萬元至億元不等。案件雖交由中區警署重案組跟進，但他認為警方愛理不理，僅記錄苦主簡單資料，擔心被低估案件嚴重性。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，投資公司沒持有投資債券或證券牌照，並走法律漏洞，聲稱是「幫熟人購買」，利用一眾親戚朋友的信任，有苦主更因看見穩定回報而把物業加按套現投資，怎料陷入金融詐騙，最後「連渣都冇！」<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎也表示，若事件涉及非法集資行為，以失實陳述及無牌協助購買結構性產品，屬刑事罪行，呼籲警方、證監會及金管局盡快處理事件，包括凍結投資公司戶口及通知所有受害人；政府也需加強相關方面公眾教育，以防更多市民墮入投資陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/265463/%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8E%A5%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E6%8C%87200%E5%90%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%99-%E6%B6%89%E6%AC%BE10%E5%84%84-%E8%8B%A6%E4%B8%BB%E6%96%A5%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F265463%2F%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%258C%2587200%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A8%2599-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25AC%25BE10%25E5%2584%2584-%25E8%258B%25A6%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2596%25A5%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A8%2599%25E6%25A1%2588&d=XJlrGENh4tChnQbLgu56%2FTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=08132dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/265463/%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8E%A5%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E6%8C%87200%E5%90%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%99-%E6%B6%89%E6%AC%BE10%E5%84%84-%E8%8B%A6%E4%B8%BB%E6%96%A5%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%A8%99%E6%A1%88</a>"},{"pid":"062c30c6483213e9152fcb7268449a2655bde118","tid":922164,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"認識一名投資公司負責人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賴</span>先生</span>，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03052328c7e84e3bbb23990684aa5ce1d0fbd57","tid":922164,"uid":18569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"邊有咁著數嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以咪話，港豬啲錢真喺易呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班都想發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8d29aee0bbfa964125e12e057ff38e01f62e27","tid":922164,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"貪字得個貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06648df6850d88f9540bb6dfe8521ad445e3b411","tid":922164,"uid":65984,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"12厘無風險, 任何一個Funds直接幫佢買哂啦, 洗搵你地雞仔米注<br />\n人唔貪心唔會俾人呃, 當買個教訓啦"},{"pid":"53a06d81972e1256cd77ace6c738a0973432491f","tid":922164,"uid":20809,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"點解d撚樣成日自己蠢都要賴人呃佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n輸錢就出黎喊苦喊忽，又話俾人呃左血汗錢"},{"pid":"2d0ac4685eedad3c8cef0284ffff02c3792dae43","tid":922164,"uid":33241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06648df6850d88f9540bb6dfe8521ad445e3b411","tid":922164,"uid":65984,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"12厘無風險, 任何一個Funds直接幫佢買哂啦, 洗搵你地雞仔米注<br />\n人唔貪心唔會俾人呃, 當買個教訓啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9caad62ea5f83276804a27d12b558bd6a16460","tid":922164,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/231237_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f